cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper deals with reinforcement learning, specifically policy gradient methods, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also deals with optimization and approximation, which are relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), respectively.
